#Text=I would go in there and do just the opposite .
#Text=I would make sure that was separated .
#Text=People set their own index .
#Text=Make it open .
#Text=Right now these things are traded secretly .
#Text=Put it out there just like any other stock exchange , and make sure that when people bet money that they got the resources to cover it one way or the other .
#Text=I mean , you do n't let people go to Las Vegas with two dollars and make a ten dollar bet .
#Text=We should n't let these people do it either , especially when where we 're guaranteeing it .
#Text=But Obama is and the man is weakening for Wall Street .
#Text=( ( WSS ) ) Do you believe Obama has done any good things as president ?
#Text=If [ Obama ] would just educate the people like I could , he would get people on his side and he would win an election based on a populist economic view
#Text=Wolfe : Well , I think it was good doing away with do n't ask , do n't tell .
#Text=I think the stimulus was a good start but it was n't very effective because it was n't enough .
#Text=He 's been too cautious about a lot of things .
#Text=He tried to increase the taxes on the very well-to-do .
#Text=The top one fifth own 94 percent of financial wealth in this country .
#Text=They were saved by the bailouts .
#Text=They made money when the stock market went down to six thousand so they could invest low ...
#Text=People like that who were saved and benefited by these trillion dollar bailouts should be the ones paying higher tax rates now , but Obama has n't emphasized that point .
#Text=He has not instructed people .
#Text=He is n't going out there and telling people the stuff I 'm telling you .
#Text=If he would just educate the people like I could , he would get people on his side and he would win an election based on a populist economic view .
#Text=People get back to work and people make money and people are empowered then businesses make more money too .
#Text=It 's not like we want to nationalize resources and take away private capital .
#Text=We just want to work with feet .
#Text=The end of the economy is the betterment of the people and not just the accumulation of capital and casino capitalism .
#Text=It 's not that .
#Text=You know it 's the betterment of people .
#Text=Capitalism is a means to an end .
#Text=It 's not the ends itself .
#Text=Human needs are not cyclical .

#Text=Economic cycles of the economy can be cyclical , but that 's why you have to have fair taxes , an interventionist government to make sure that society works for the people and Obama 's not doing that .
#Text=The man has failed .
